<h2 class='date-header'><span>Sunday, April 13, 2014</span></h2>

          <div class="date-posts">
        
<div class='post-outer'>
<div class='post hentry'>
<a name='202506597712290873'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title'>
<a href='http://iteadthomam.blogspot.com/2014/04/collection-of-essays-on-garrigou.html' target='_blank'>Collection of Essays on Garrigou-Lagrange</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content'>
<div>
<fb:like action='like' colorscheme='light' font='arial' href='http://iteadthomam.blogspot.com/2014/04/collection-of-essays-on-garrigou.html' layout='standard' send='true' show_faces='false'></fb:like>
</div>
<br/><a class='a2a_dd' href='http://www.addtoany.com/share_save'><img alt='Share/Bookmark' border='0' height='16' src='http://static.addtoany.com/buttons/share_save_171_16.png' width='171'/></a><p class='a2a_linkname_escape' style='display:none'>Collection of Essays on Garrigou-Lagrange</p><script type='text/javascript'>var a2a_config = a2a_config || {};a2a_config.linkname_escape=1;a2a_config.linkurl="http://iteadthomam.blogspot.com/2014/04/collection-of-essays-on-garrigou.html";</script><script src='http://static.addtoany.com/menu/page.js' type='text/javascript'></script>
<br />
<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
<a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-wHUR2WdJg98/U0rTXMufOjI/AAAAAAAACk0/4NkUhci0-lQ/s1600/Crean+et+al.+(eds).+-+Reginald+Garrigou-Lagrange,+Teacher+of+Thomism+(cover).jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-wHUR2WdJg98/U0rTXMufOjI/AAAAAAAACk0/4NkUhci0-lQ/s1600/Crean+et+al.+(eds).+-+Reginald+Garrigou-Lagrange,+Teacher+of+Thomism+(cover).jpg" height="400" width="305" /></a></div>
<br />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<span style="color: #990000; font-family: Georgia, Times New Roman, serif;"><b>Jude Chua Soo Meng, Thomas Crean OP (Eds.)&nbsp;</b></span></div>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<span style="color: #990000; font-family: Georgia, Times New Roman, serif;"><b><i>Reginald Garrigou-Lagrange OP: Teacher of Thomism</i>. &nbsp;</b></span></div>
<div style="text-align: center;">
